                                <div class="service-block" style="visibility: visible;">
                                  
                                    <div class="text-block">
                                        <div class="name">Cutting-Edge Technology</div>
                                        <div class="info">
                                            The smart home company utilizes state-of-the-art technologies, including advanced sensors, smart devices, and cloud-based platforms, to deliver reliable, secure, and scalable smart home solutions that meet the evolving needs of clients.
                                        </div>
                                       
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-md-4">
                                <div class="service-block" style="visibility: visible;">
                                  
                                    <div class="text-block">
                                        <div class="name">Professional Installation and Support</div>
                                        <div class="info">The smart home company provides professional installation, setup, and ongoing support for their smart home systems, ensuring a hassle-free experience for clients and maximizing the performance and longevity of the smart home ecosystem.</div>
                                       
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

