                    </div>
                </div><!-- End Icon Box -->

                <div class="icon-box d-flex position-relative" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <i class="ri-check-double-line"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Personalized comfort and expandability</h4>
                        <p>Clients can customize settings, enjoy seamless entertainment, and expand their smart home system as needed, creating a personalized and future-proofed home experience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div><!-- End Icon Box -->

            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
